body_html:
I have checked the linker and everything looks fine, apart from:
wsock32.lib
ws2_32.lib
shlwapi.lib
advapi32.lib

I got rid of them, because they haven´t been created, and tensorflow is not complaing about them.

The issue see in:
1>c_api.cc.obj : error LNK2019: tensorflow::ops::BuildWhileLoop ...
1>while_gradients.obj : error LNK2001: tensorflow::ops::BuildWhileLoop ...
1>cuda_dnn.obj : error LNK2019: símbolo externo cudnnConvolutionBiasActivationForward ...
1>cuda_dnn.obj : error LNK2019: símbolo externo cudnnSetRNNDescriptor_v6 ...
1>C:\Demos\TF_DLL_GPU\tensorflow\tensorflow\contrib\cmake\build\Release\tensorflow.dll : fatal error LNK1120: 3 externos sin resolver

The the libraries tf_c.lib, tf_cc.lib and tf_stream_executer have been created correctly, so not sure why tensorflow is complaying about c_api.cc , while_gradients and cuda_dnn.

Any ideas how to fix this issue?

Thanks for your time.

Thanks for your time.
